      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait 1000mg every 4 hours?? that seems like a lot. i read online that taking too much ibuprofen can mess up your stomach or kidneys. are you sure it's safe to take that much so often? i'm kinda scared of getting an ulcer or something.",
